.SH Changes
.SS Vera++ 1.2.1
.PP
Vera++ 1.2.1 differs from 1.2.0 in the following ways:
.IP \[bu] 2
BUGFIX: fix \f[C]\-\-inputs\f[] in order to be able to read the inputs
